# How to load the model?
# 1. Open a new terminal ( Git Bash, Command Prompt or similar || PowerShell doesn't work! )
# 2. Spawn poetry shell with the command: poetry shell
# 2. cd to ./model_setup/ 
# 4. Make the .sh file executable with the command: chmod +x o_llava_phi3_3b_4k_q4-create_model.sh
# 5. Run the .sh file with the command: ./o_llava_phi3_3b_4k_q4-create_model.sh

